msgid "Hero Service"
msgstr "Servicio de Héroes"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2022-02-22-quarkus-superheroes-to-the-rescue.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Hero service is a fully reactive and non-blocking HTTP microservice exposing CRUD operations on a `+Hero+` data model. The REST layer is implemented using https://quarkus.io/guides/resteasy-reactive[RESTEasy Reactive^] with reactive endpoints. Data is persisted into a https://www.postgresql.org[PostgreSQL^] database using the https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache#solution-2-using-the-repository-pattern[repository pattern^] from https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache[Quarkus Hibernate Reactive with Panache^]. Additionally, the Hero service favors https://quarkus.io/guides/cdi-reference#simplified-constructor-injection[constructor injection^] of beans over https://quarkus.io/guides/cdi-reference#qualified-injected-fields[field injection^]. The Hero service contains a full suite of unit and integration tests, using https://quarkus.io/guides/getting-started-testing#further-simplification-with-injectmock[mocking^], https://quarkus.io/guides/getting-started-testing#using-spies-instead-of-mocks-with-injectspy[spying^], and testing within https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache#transactions[isolated transactions^]."
msgstr "El servicio Hero es un microservicio HTTP totalmente reactivo y no bloqueante que expone operaciones CRUD en un modelo de datos `Hero`. La capa REST se implementa utilizando  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/resteasy-reactive[RESTEasy Reactive, window=_blank] con puntos finales reactivos. Los datos se persisten en una base de datos  link:https://www.postgresql.org[PostgreSQL, window=_blank] utilizando el  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache#solution-2-using-the-repository-pattern[patrón de repositorio, window=_blank] de  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache[Quarkus Hibernate Reactive con Panache, window=_blank]. Además, el servicio Hero favorece la  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/cdi-reference#simplified-constructor-injection[inyección de constructores, window=_blank] de beans sobre  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/cdi-reference#qualified-injected-fields[la inyección de campos, window=_blank]. El servicio Hero contiene un conjunto completo de pruebas unitarias y de integración, utilizando  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/getting-started-testing#further-simplification-with-injectmock[mocking, window=_blank],  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/getting-started-testing#using-spies-instead-of-mocks-with-injectspy[spying, window=_blank] y pruebas dentro de  link:https://quarkus.io/guides/hibernate-reactive-panache#transactions[transacciones aisladas, window=_blank]."

